  "pages": [
    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Estimats on the total attendance\nat the Interstate fair for the two\nweeks closing tonight place the\nfigure at close to 100000 More\nthan 100000 paid admissions had\nbeen recorded up to last night and\ntoday's crowd, it is figured, will not\nfall short of $4,000.\n\n\nCompared with last years at\ntendance Of approximately $4,000.\nthis years fair Is the greatest in\npoint of patronage in the history of\nthe Interstate exposition.\n\n\nIn spite of the big attendance,\nhowever. it Is not believd that this\nvars profits will greatly exceed the\n$4,000 cleared last year, expenses\nof the present fair being greatly\nincreasd."
    }
  ]
